---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Kalyan AI | Bespoke hosted AI systems partner"
	description="Meet Kalyan AI and how we design, build, and host bespoke AI systems with clear ownership, governance, and ongoing support for your organisation."
>
	<main class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-5xl flex-col gap-10 px-6 pb-14">
		<section class="ka-card mx-auto max-w-5xl space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">About</h1>
			<p class="copy-narrow max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg text-[var(--primary)]">
				We build and host bespoke AI systems that remove friction from core business workflows.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-4 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<div class="mx-auto aspect-[4/4.5] w-full max-w-md overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] shadow-sm">
				<img
					class="h-full w-full object-cover"
					src="/images/1761512653.png"
					alt="Zax Kalyan"
					loading="lazy"
					decoding="async"
					style="object-position: 50% 12%;"
				/>
			</div>

			<div class="space-y-3 text-center">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Founder</h2>
				<div class="space-y-3 !text-center">
					<div class="space-y-1">
						<p class="hidden text-xs font-bold text-[var(--primary)] md:hidden">Founder background</p>
						<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">
							I’m Zax Kalyan, founder of Kalyan AI. I’ve spent <span class="font-bold">15+ years</span> leading and growing businesses under real-world pressure — <span class="font-bold">owning P&L</span>, building teams, and delivering results across industries.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-1">
						<p class="hidden text-xs font-bold text-[var(--primary)] md:hidden">The philosophy behind Kalyan AI</p>
						<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">
							Kalyan AI is built around a simple idea: <span class="font-bold">bespoke AI systems</span> should fit the way your business actually runs. We design, build, and host systems that turn messy inputs into <span class="font-bold">clear outputs</span> — so decisions, follow-ups, and reporting happen reliably, with proper ownership and oversight.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-1">
						<p class="hidden text-xs font-bold text-[var(--primary)] md:hidden">Nuvo Labs and how it informs decisions</p>
						<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">
							I’m also a contributor and shareholder at Nuvo Labs, a deep-tech AI research company. That proximity to research helps inform the technical choices we make, while keeping delivery focused on what matters day-to-day: <span class="font-bold">reliability, control, and measurable impact</span>.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">What we do</h2>
			<div class="space-y-2 !text-center">
				<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">
					We design, build, and operate hosted AI systems that respect how your business already works. Each system is <span class="font-bold">tailored to your data, decisions, and owners</span>—so your team gains clarity without more tools to manage.
				</p>
				<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">
					You keep control and oversight; we handle the <span class="font-bold">engineering, hosting, and steady improvements</span>.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">How we work</h2>
			<ol class="space-y-2 text-[var(--muted)] text-center list-none">
				<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Discover:</span> We map your current workflows, data, and <span class="font-bold">decision points</span>.</li>
				<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Build:</span> We assemble the hosted AI layer with safeguards and <span class="font-bold">clear ownership</span>.</li>
				<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Deploy:</span> We launch with you, monitor outcomes, and keep the system dependable.</li>
				<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Improve:</span> We refine prompts, data flows, and <span class="font-bold">reporting based on real usage</span>.</li>
			</ol>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">What you get</h2>
			<ul class="space-y-2 text-[var(--muted)] text-center list-none">
				<li><span class="font-medium text-[var(--primary)]">Discovery and system design</span> — map workflows, inputs, decisions, and <span class="font-bold">owners</span>.</li>
				<li><span class="font-medium text-[var(--primary)]">Build and integration</span> — connect to your data and <span class="font-bold">operational tools</span>.</li>
				<li><span class="font-medium text-[var(--primary)]">Hosted operation</span> — monitoring, reliability, and <span class="font-bold">steady improvements</span>.</li>
				<li><span class="font-medium text-[var(--primary)]">Training and handover</span> — your team knows how to use it day one.</li>
				<li><span class="font-medium text-[var(--primary)]">Ongoing support</span> — fixes, refinements, and <span class="font-bold">iteration</span> based on real usage.</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">What you can expect</h2>
			<ul class="space-y-2 text-[var(--muted)] text-center list-none">
				<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Clarity</span> on decisions, owners, and timing.</li>
				<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Speed</span> without sacrificing oversight or compliance.</li>
				<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Reliability</span> from a hosted system that stays maintained and supported.</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<div class="text-center">
			<a
				class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-[var(--secondary)]"
				href="/contact#book"
				data-plausible="BookACall"
			>
				Book a call
			</a>
		</div>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">FAQs</h2>
			<div class="divide-y divide-[var(--border-subtle)] rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border-subtle)] bg-white/80 text-center">
				{[
					{
						q: 'What types of businesses do you work with?',
						a: 'SMEs where operations rely on people making repeat decisions from calls, documents, and pipelines. We focus on teams that value clarity and control.',
					},
					{
						q: 'How quickly can we ship a first version?',
						a: 'Most first versions go live in 2–4 weeks once we have access to your processes and data examples. We keep the initial scope tight to show value early.',
					},
					{
						q: 'Do you host the system for us?',
						a: 'Yes. We host, monitor, and maintain the system so you do not need extra infrastructure or support staff to keep it reliable.',
					},
					{
						q: 'What about data security and access control?',
						a: 'We set clear data boundaries, least-privilege access, and audit trails. Ownership and permissions stay defined for your team.',
					},
					{
						q: 'Can this connect to our existing tools and workflows?',
						a: 'Yes. We integrate with your current systems and processes so the hosted AI layer fits how you already work.',
					},
					{
						q: 'How do pricing and ongoing support work?',
						a: 'We scope a build fee for the first version, then provide a hosting and support plan that covers monitoring, fixes, and iterative improvements.',
					},
					{
						q: 'What do you need from us to get started?',
						a: 'Access to the people, examples, and systems that show how you work today, plus a clear owner for decisions. We handle the rest.',
					},
				].map((item) => (
					<details class="group px-4 py-3 text-[var(--muted)]">
						<summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-center gap-2 text-center text-[var(--brand-navy)] font-semibold transition hover:text-[var(--brand-navy-light)] focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-[var(--primary)] focus-visible:ring-offset-0">
							<span>{item.q}</span>
							<span class="text-sm text-[var(--muted)] group-open:rotate-45 transition">+</span>
						</summary>
						<div class="pt-2 text-[var(--muted)] text-center">
							<p>{item.a}</p>
						</div>
					</details>
				))}
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
